{
  "lesson": "WC-01-03",
  "audioMaster": "training/module01-foundations/WC-01-03-full-narration-v1.0.mp3",
  "audioDurationS": 156.918,
  "method": "silencedetect -32dB/0.28s within known block windows; proportional fallback",
  "phrases": [
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p01",
      "text": "WashCentral watches for inactivity.",
      "startS": 0,
      "endS": 2.185,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p02",
      "text": "Leave a session untouched and it does not drop you cold.",
      "startS": 2.514,
      "endS": 5.658,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p03",
      "text": "It warns you first, right over whatever page you left open.",
      "startS": 5.982,
      "endS": 9.505,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p04",
      "text": "Today that's the Command Center.",
      "startS": 9.791,
      "endS": 11.477,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p05",
      "text": "Watch the lower corner.",
      "startS": 11.92,
      "endS": 13.232,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p06",
      "text": "A small toast slides in: Session expiring soon, auto log-out in two minutes,",
      "startS": 13.607,
      "endS": 15.285,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p07",
      "text": "with a Stay Active button.",
      "startS": 15.761,
      "endS": 20.774,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p08",
      "text": "It's the compact version of the warning, easy to miss if you're looking away.",
      "startS": 21.294,
      "endS": 25.035,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p09",
      "text": "At the same moment, a dialog opens dead center.",
      "startS": 25.502,
      "endS": 28.3,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p10",
      "text": "Still there? it asks.",
      "startS": 28.833,
      "endS": 30.236,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p11",
      "text": "Two minutes remaining, counting down.",
      "startS": 30.811,
      "endS": 32.737,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p12",
      "text": "The line underneath tells you exactly how to stay: move your mouse or press any key.",
      "startS": 33.416,
      "endS": 38.48,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p13",
      "text": "Two buttons sit on the dialog.",
      "startS": 38.955,
      "endS": 40.627,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p14",
      "text": "Stay Logged In keeps you signed in and returns you to your work.",
      "startS": 41.097,
      "endS": 44.642,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p15",
      "text": "Log Out Now ends the session right away.",
      "startS": 45.203,
      "endS": 47.741,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p16",
      "text": "That one is a real logout, so leave it alone unless you mean to sign out.",
      "startS": 48.169,
      "endS": 52.334,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p17",
      "text": "So what if you ignore it?",
      "startS": 52.8,
      "endS": 55.241,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p18",
      "text": "At zero, the session closes and returns you to the sign-in page.",
      "startS": 55.241,
      "endS": 59.599,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p19",
      "text": "How long it may sit idle before the warning starts is set per user level,",
      "startS": 59.599,
      "endS": 63.884,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p20",
      "text": "and the exact figure for the demo login is still being pinned down.",
      "startS": 63.884,
      "endS": 67.599,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p21",
      "text": "Staying in is easy.",
      "startS": 68,
      "endS": 69.385,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p22",
      "text": "Move the mouse, tap a key, or click Stay Logged In.",
      "startS": 69.693,
      "endS": 70.559,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p23",
      "text": "The countdown stops, the dialog clears, and you pick up exactly where you were.",
      "startS": 70.765,
      "endS": 78.374,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p24",
      "text": "Stay Active on the toast does the same job.",
      "startS": 78.707,
      "endS": 81.52,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p25",
      "text": "Now, where does that timer come from?",
      "startS": 81.92,
      "endS": 83.88,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p26",
      "text": "Open Settings from the left rail and choose User Levels.",
      "startS": 85.279,
      "endS": 88.759,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p27",
      "text": "The breadcrumb reads Settings, then User Levels.",
      "startS": 89.312,
      "endS": 92.279,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p28",
      "text": "This page sets the idle limit for every level of user.",
      "startS": 93.012,
      "endS": 96.214,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p29",
      "text": "Across the top, three summary tiles.",
      "startS": 96.726,
      "endS": 99.067,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p30",
      "text": "Total Levels, Max Security Level, and Longest Timeout in minutes.",
      "startS": 99.463,
      "endS": 100.291,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p31",
      "text": "Today they read fourteen, twenty, and a hundred and twenty.",
      "startS": 100.63,
      "endS": 103.729,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p32",
      "text": "Fourteen levels, and the longest idle window runs two full hours.",
      "startS": 104.226,
      "endS": 112.189,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p33",
      "text": "The table has three columns.",
      "startS": 112.64,
      "endS": 114.354,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p34",
      "text": "Name, Security Level, and Session Timeout in minutes.",
      "startS": 114.76,
      "endS": 115.191,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p35",
      "text": "That last column is the one to know:",
      "startS": 115.565,
      "endS": 118.511,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p36",
      "text": "it's how many idle minutes a level gets before the Still there? countdown begins.",
      "startS": 119.233,
      "endS": 125.812,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p37",
      "text": "The numbers run from five minutes up to a hundred and twenty.",
      "startS": 126.32,
      "endS": 129.708,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p38",
      "text": "Cashiers and the lower levels sit at five;",
      "startS": 130.296,
      "endS": 132.606,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p39",
      "text": "administrators and service roles at a hundred and twenty.",
      "startS": 132.888,
      "endS": 135.678,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p40",
      "text": "So a cashier logged out after five idle minutes isn't hitting a bug.",
      "startS": 136.209,
      "endS": 140.357,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p41",
      "text": "That's the setting doing its job.",
      "startS": 140.578,
      "endS": 142.38,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s11",
      "id": "p42",
      "text": "So when a manager says the system logs them out every few minutes, you know the move.",
      "startS": 142.857,
      "endS": 147.409,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s11",
      "id": "p43",
      "text": "Open User Levels, find their level under Name, and read its Session Timeout.",
      "startS": 147.906,
      "endS": 152.389,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s11",
      "id": "p44",
      "text": "A small number is the whole answer, and you never touch the row.",
      "startS": 152.778,
      "endS": 156.471,
      "timing": "silence"
    }
  ]
}